    "details": "The Exim development team reports:\n\n> All installations having Exim set-uid root and using \\'perl_startup\\'\n> are vulnerable to a local privilege escalation. Any user who can start\n> an instance of Exim (and this is normally **any** user) can gain root\n> privileges. If you do not use \\'perl_startup\\' you **should** be safe.\n",
